  "text": "3) Acoustic Source Localization: Acoustic source localization can be realized by calculating the spatial power spectrum given by [CITATION_1] where is the output signal of delay-and-sum beamforming for the steering direction and is the time averaging operation. If the steering direction is equal to the wavefront arrival direction , the output power of delay-and-sum beamforming is maximized. Therefore, the wavefront arrival direction can be estimated by finding the maximum value of the spatial power spectrum. When there are multiple sound sources, the wavefront arrival directions can also be estimated by finding the peak values of the spatial power spectrum.",
